@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC / Backoffice Operator" as Actor
participant ":System" as System

== Update Route ==
activate Actor
Actor -> System : updateRoute(routeId, distance, estimatedFlightTime, minimumRange, minimumCapacity, changeReason)
activate System
note right of System: The system validates the input,\ncloses the current version,\nand creates a new RouteVersion.
System --> Actor : informs operation success and returns updated route
deactivate System
deactivate Actor

== Deactivate Route ==
Actor -> System : deactivateRoute(routeId)
activate System
note right of System: The system marks the route as inactive.\nThe route is NOT deleted.
System --> Actor : informs operation success (204 No Content)
deactivate System
deactivate Actor
@enduml
